Global setup:
  git config --global user.email your@email.net
      

Next steps:
  mkdir supong
  cd supong
  git init
  touch README
  git add README
  git commit -m 'first commit'
  git remote add origin git@github.com:fbern/supong.git
  git push origin master
      

Push into Existing Git Repo?
  cd existing_git_repo
  git remote add origin git@github.com:fbern/supong.git
  git push origin master
      
Checkout existing Git Repo
  mkdir whatever_you_want
  cd whatever_you_want
  git clone git://github.com/fbern/supong.git
